explanation: A section of a document showing ‘ARTICLE INFO’ including article history (dates received, revised, accepted, published online) and keywords (influenza vaccine, baculovirus expression, recombinant protein, clinical trials). does not support the claim – the image only shows article metadata and keywords, with no information on HA antigen content or comparative immunogenicity of Flublok.
